<h1>Fee Policies</h1>
<hr>

<h3>
  General fees
</h3>
<p>
  Creating a PickCoin Exchange account is free of charge.
</p>
<p>
  Storing cryptocurrencies in PickCoin Exchange's secure vaults is free of charge.
</p>

<br>
<h3>
  Exchange Trading fees
</h3>
<p>
  Default trade fee is 0% per each market pair.
</p>

<br>
<h3>
  Deposit and Withdrawal fees
</h3>
<p>
  Cryptocurrency deposits are free of charge and there is a minimum deposit amount.
  <br>
  There is a nominal charge for cryptocurrency withdrawals to cover miner fees.
</p>
